  - dialogueIndex: 1
    choices:
    - "\u201CT\xF4i kh\xF4ng s\u1EE3 ma v\u1EADt. C\xF3 chuy\u1EC7n g\xEC v\u1EADy?\u201D"
    - "\u201CT\xF4i ch\u1EC9 mu\u1ED1n ngh\u1EC9 ng\u01A1i, kh\xF4ng d\xEDnh l\xEDu
      v\xE0o r\u1EAFc r\u1ED1i.\u201D"
    - "\u201CMa v\u1EADt? \xDD c\xF4 l\xE0 l\u0169 n\xE0o?\u201D"
